# NOTE: this single-file .env.example was retired in favor of one .env per
# service in the cockpit bundle. Use these instead:
#
#   cp alfred-coo.env.example  alfred-coo.env
#   cp soul-svc.env.example    soul-svc.env
#
# See BUNDLE_README.md for the full setup walkthrough.
#
# Single-service users (running just `alfred-coo` without the rest of the
# bundle) can still source alfred-coo.env directly via `--env-file` or by
# running `docker compose up alfred-coo` after copying soul-svc.env.example.
